	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Which mapper does the Super Mario Bros. + Tetris + Nintendo World Cup use?  I can't get the game to work consistently on emulators.  #47 gives some partial results, is there a better one to try?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
