	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The game uses a unique mapper, though whoever dumped it never bothered reverse-engineering it (probably just desoldered the ROMs instead).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

